Okay then. Next time you are playing rank. Send me a tell. I will go ADC and get 20 CS by 10 mins then on top of that. I will die at least 4 times before the 10 min mark.

Then you can tell me how a great support can carry. Then show me how you do it. When top is doing this also. As well as middle or jungle or BOTH.

I look forward to hear from you.{{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}}
